So I will start with a little culture and recommend the Duomo di Milano - a lace like exterior and simply incredible interior. The perfect place to sit and think. However, if you feel a bit more touristy then the Arco della Pace should be on your satnav and hereâ€™s some gossip; the horses are positioned to show their didietros- or as I have learned to say in Malta, their patatas :)</p>

