<p>Staying in the <a href="https://www.nh-hotels.it/hotel/nh-milano-congress-centre" target="_blank">NH Hotel Milano Congress</a>, which is part of the  biggest conference centre in Milan, was perfect me on this trip. Fully refurbished in 2015, the rooms are beautifully light and airy with comfortable beds and lovely bathrooms.</p>

